PermissionService.WriteRelationshipsRequest
public static final class PermissionService.WriteRelationshipsRequest.Builder extends com.google.protobuf.GeneratedMessageV3.Builder<PermissionService.WriteRelationshipsRequest.Builder> implements PermissionService.WriteRelationshipsRequestOrBuilder
 WriteRelationshipsRequest contains a list of Relationship mutations that
 should be applied to the service. If the optional_preconditions parameter
 is included, all of the specified preconditions must also be satisfied before
 the write will be committed.
